文|《财经》数据研究员 徐进图|《财经》视觉中心 编辑|谢丽容1.全国累计新增确诊病例图1由图可见，国内非湖北地区正趋于平缓。
As can be seen from the chart, China's non-Hubei province is leveling off. & # 160; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45; & # 45;
2. 新增病例：国内非湖北地区继续坚定下降，有望近日归零图2国内非湖北新增病例继续坚定下降。
2. New cases: China's non-Hubei region continues to decline firmly, and the number of non-Hubei new cases is expected to fall firmly in recent days.
新增量基本归零指日可待。
New increments are almost at zero.
有网友问为什么要说“坚定”下降？须知一个R0值2-3的传染病如果没有得到有效控制，一定是不断加速以爆炸方式增长。
Some netizens have asked why there is such a thing as a "steady" decline? An infectious disease with an R0 value of 2-3, if not effectively controlled, must be growing at an accelerating rate.
按新冠病毒潜伏期中位值4天估算，以武汉封城为节点，经过大约10余天，2月3日开始本应到了可能出现第二、三代甚至第四代病例叠加爆发的时候，我们却看到国内非湖北地区新增病例不但没有继续增加反而开始回落。
According to the median incubation period of the new crown virus 4 days, Wuhan sealing as the node, after about 10 days, February 3 should have appeared the second, third or even fourth generation of cases of the superimposition of the outbreak, we see that the non-Hubei region of China has not continued to increase the number of new cases but began to fall.
那只能得出一个结论，就是病毒传播路径被有效阻断了。
That only leads to the conclusion that the virus propagation path is effectively blocked.
这都是防控措施得力到位的结果，所以我们用了“坚定”二字。
This is the result of effective control measures in place, so we used the word "firm."
其实像这种量级的疫情只能有两种状态：控制住了还是没控制住。
There are only two conditions for an epidemic of this magnitude: under control or out of control.
没控制住就会迅速爆发，很短时间内就会达到数字无法遮盖的地步。
If unchecked, it will erupt quickly, reaching a point where numbers cannot be covered in a very short time.
控制住了就是控制住了。
It's under control. It's under control.
形势就会比较快地好转。
The situation will improve relatively quickly.
我们对非湖北地区控制疫情已经有了坚定信心。
We have firm confidence in controlling the epidemic in non-Hubei areas.
图3有读者问，湖北数据为什么不从2月12日切换到新口径。
Fig. 3 has readers asking why Hubei data did not switch to new calibres from Feb. 12.
因为，2月12日湖北发布的13332例临床诊断病例未分别此前的存量的当日的增量，无论往前还是往后都不具可比性。
For the 13,332 cases of clinical diagnosis issued in Hubei on February 12 did not account for the increase in previous stocks on the same day, and were not comparable either forward or later.
所以我们从13日开始切换。
So we switched from 13th to 13th.
但无论按老口径还是新口径，湖北非武汉地区的数字都好得让人不太敢信，接下来的趋势，不妨明天再看。
But in both old and new calibres, the figures for Hubei non-Wuhan are too good to be believed, and the next trend should be looked at tomorrow.
图4武汉按新口径下降，按老口径略有增长，待观察。
Fig. 4 Wuhan descends according to new caliber, increase slightly according to old caliber, wait to see.
3. 确诊病例增速：国内非湖北地区增速继续下降至2%以下，大概率在2月20日前后归零图5武汉和湖北非武汉地区新口径增速有所回归。
3. Growth rate of confirmed cases: China's non-Hubei region continued to decline to less than 2%, the high probability before and after February 20 to zero Figure 5 Wuhan and Hubei non-Wuhan areas of the new caliber growth rate has returned.
其中湖北非武汉地区增速按老口径降至2%以下，未免过于乐观，暂不采用。
Among them, Hubei non-Wuhan area growth rate fell to 2% according to the old caliber, not too optimistic, temporarily not to adopt.
湖北整体变动趋势仍待观察。
The overall change trend in Hubei remains to be seen.
国内非湖北地区增速降至2%以内，有望近日归零。
Domestic non-Hubei region growth rate fell to less than 2%, is expected to close recently.
4.国内非湖北地区追踪力度加大，存量继续下降图6国内非湖北地区对密切接触者追踪力度持续加大。
The domestic non-Hubei area tracking intensity increases, the stock continues to decline Fig. 6 Domestic non-Hubei area to the close contact trace strength continues to increase.
图7国内非湖北地区的该项存量，随疫情缓解而持续下降。
Fig. 7 The stock in non-Hubei area of China continued to decrease as the epidemic subsided.
5.新增疑似病例和疑似病例存量图8国内非湖北地区的新增疑似病例连日来不断下降。
New Suspected Cases and Suspected Cases Inventory Figure 8 New suspected cases in non-Hubei areas of China have been decreasing for several days.
湖北昨天略有回升。
Hubei recovered slightly yesterday.
图9湖北虽然新增疑似病例增加，但由于排查力度加大，待排查疑似病例继续连续下降。
Fig. 9 Although the number of new suspected cases increased in Hubei Province, the number of suspected cases continued to decrease due to the intensive screening.
国内非湖北地区下降。
Domestic non-Hubei region declined.
6.国内非湖北地区在院治疗人数见顶图10今我们改用“全国现有确诊人数-湖北现有确诊人数”推出“国内非湖北地区现有确诊人数”，并因为考虑到非湖北地区基本做到“尽收尽治”，直接以此替代“国内非湖北在院治疗人数”。
The number of people admitted to hospitals in non-Hubei areas of China has been replaced by the number of people diagnosed in non-Hubei areas in China. The number of people diagnosed in non-Hubei areas in China has been replaced by the number of people treated in non-Hubei hospitals in China.
我们看到非湖北地区在院人数2月11日以后已连续出下降。
We have seen that the number of hospital residents in non-Hubei areas has declined continuously since Feb. 11.
与此同时，我们看到湖北仍有“确诊但未在医院”的病例。
At the same time, we still see "confirmed but not in hospital" cases in Hubei.
相信他们虽然不在医院却已得到妥善隔离和医疗救助。
They are believed to have been properly quarantined and given medical assistance while not in hospital.
7.新增治愈和病死率图11新增治愈数继续上升。
7. The number of new treatments added to figure 11 continues to rise.
湖北新治愈人数一度跳升，有口径转换因素，也有存量划转因素。
Hubei the number of newly cured people once jumped, there are caliber conversion factors, there are also stock transfer factors.
图12国内非湖北地区新增治愈与新增确诊人数已于2月12日成功越过“黄金交叉”点。
Fig. 12 The number of newly diagnosed and cured cases in non-Hubei areas of China successfully crossed the Golden Cross on February 12.
意味着从这一天起，若不出意外，国内非湖北地区近10000例在院治疗者将开始逐步减少。
This means that from this day, if no accident, the nearly 10,000 patients in non-Hubei region of China will start to gradually reduce.
在此之前，国内非湖北地区的另外两个重要存量“尚在接受医学观察人数”和“待排查疑似病例”皆已先后见顶下降。
Before that, the other two important stocks in non-Hubei areas of China "are still under medical observation" and "pending investigation of suspected cases" have all peaked.
由于这三大存量（我们在数说疫情0211曾有阐述）都对应着巨大医疗资源和社会资源，它们的全面见顶下降，毫无疑问是关乎整个战局态势的“关键拐点”！图13按照新口径，湖北地区病死率有所降低，应是“临床诊断病例”总体上比原“确诊病例”病情较轻、病死率较低所致。
The overall decline in these three stocks, which we have described in case 0211, represents a "key inflection point" for the whole situation. Figure 13 shows a decrease in the mortality rate of Hubei Province.
国内非湖北地区病死率仍在缓慢提升，亦属正常：因为疫情暴发初期，每日入院新增病例猛增，经过一段时间滞后，随病程进展会带来死亡人数的较快增加；与此同时，随着疫情得到控制，每日新增确诊病例会出现明显下降，累计确诊增速放缓。
The rate of death in non-Hubei areas of the country is still slowly rising and normal: the number of new hospitalizations surges daily at the beginning of the outbreak, with a time lag leading to a faster increase in the number of deaths as the disease progresses; at the same time, with the outbreak under control, there will be a significant decrease in daily confirmed cases, slowing the cumulative rate of confirmed cases.
这一快（分子），一慢（分母），会导致病死率缓慢回升。
This fast (molecular), a slow (denominator), will lead to a slow recovery in the death rate.
只有在疫情基本结束时，这个数值才会逼近“最终病死率”。
Only when the epidemic is largely over will this figure approach the "final fatality rate."
小结：国内非湖北地区新增病例有望在2月20日前后基本归零，也就是累计确诊病例见“顶”。
Summary: New cases in non-Hubei areas of China are expected to be nearly zero by February 20, that is, the cumulative number of confirmed cases see the "peak."
湖北、武汉进入保卫战总攻阶段。
Hubei and Wuhan entered the stage of defending the war.
